\mt1 Xon⁴xi³ qui³chji³-le⁴cho⁴ta⁴hebreos 
\c 1  
\s1 Ni³na¹ qui³si³chjen¹ je² ˀnti¹-le⁴ nca³ tsa³cja¹cao⁴-na¹ 
\p  
\v 1 Ni⁴čhjin³co²tse³ a³li² cˀoa⁴cji³ ncjin² cˀa³ Ni³na¹ tsa³cja¹cao⁴ nˀai³jcha¹cjin³-na¹. Qui³si³chjen¹ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ qui³nchja⁴ya³jin³-le⁴ nˀai³jcha¹cjin³-na¹ tˀa³tsˀe⁴. Cja⁴ˀai¹ cja⁴ˀai¹-sˀin² qui³nchja⁴.  
\v 2 Je² ni⁴čhjin³ xi³ sˀa⁴ ja³ˀa³to³ Ni³na¹ qui³nchja⁴cao⁴-na¹. Qui³si³chjen¹ je² ˀnti¹-le⁴ nca³ tsa³cja¹cao⁴-na¹. Ni³na¹ tsa³ca³sen¹nta³ je² ˀnti¹-le⁴ nca³ tsjoa¹cjoa⁴tjao²-le⁴ nca³yi³je³. Cao⁴ nca³ je² tsa³cˀe¹nta³-ni³ je² son³ˀnte³-vi⁴.  
\v 3 Ti⁴je²-ni³ Jesucristo xi³ qui³si³cˀa³tsen³ cjoa⁴je³ya³-le⁴ Ni³na¹. Cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ cjoan³-ni³ Cristo ti⁴je²-ni³ sen¹-le⁴ jo³ cjoan³ Ni³na¹. Cˀoa⁴ je² Cristo va³sen²nˀion¹-ni³ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴ cao⁴ en¹ xi³ tsˀe⁴ nca³nˀion¹-le⁴. Cˀia⁴ nca³ je³qui³si³tsje³ je¹-na¹, tsa³cˀe²jna³tˀa³-le⁴ ntsja³ nca³ qui²xi⁴ je² xi³ ti¹jna³je³ya³ ncˀa³jmi³.  
\v 4 Cristo nqui²sa⁴ ti¹tjon² coan³ cao⁴-ni³ tsa² a²ncje⁴, nca⁴ qui³tsˀai²-le⁴ jnco³ jan³ˀain¹ xi³ nqui²sa⁴ ncˀa³ cao⁴-ni³ tsa² tsˀe⁴ a²ncje⁴. 
\s1 Je² ˀnti¹-le⁴ Ni³na¹ nqui²sa⁴ ti¹tjon² coan³ cao⁴-ni³ tsa² a²ncje⁴ 
\p  
\v 5 Ni³na¹ a³ cˀoa⁴qui³tso²-le⁴ a²ncje⁴ jnco³ cˀa²: Ji³ ni¹³ ˀnti¹-na⁴. Ntˀai⁴-vi⁴ ji³ xi³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² ˀnti¹-na⁴ xin³-le²³. Nqui²jnco³cˀa²: An³ coan⁴ Nˀai³-le⁴, cˀoa⁴ je² coan⁴ ˀnti¹na⁴.  
\v 6 Cˀia⁴ nca³ va³sen¹va³sen³ je² ˀnti¹tjon² i⁴ son³ˀnte³, nqui²jnco³cˀa² tso²: Nca³tsˀi³ a²ncje⁴-le⁴ Ni³na¹, ca²ta³ve³xcon¹ nca³ je².  
\v 7 Xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ a²ncje⁴ tso²: Je² xi³ cˀoa⁴sˀin¹ a²ncje⁴-le⁴ nca³ to⁴jo³ espíritu cjoan³, cˀoa⁴ je² xi³ cˀoa⁴sˀin¹ cho⁴ˀnta³-le⁴ nca³ to⁴jo³ ni⁴jen⁴lˀi¹ cjoan³.  
\v 8 To⁴nca³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ ˀnti¹-le⁴ tso²: Je² ya¹xi²le⁴-li⁴, Ji³ Ni³na¹, jo³ nca³ntsjai² nca³ntsjai². Je² ni³se³-le⁴ cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³-li⁴, ni³se³ xi³ ntia⁴²qui²xi⁴ yˀa³.  
\v 9 Coan³tsjoa³chai³ xi³ ntia⁴²qui²xi⁴, cˀoa⁴ coan³jti³chai³ xi³ chˀao³ tjin¹. To⁴coi³ Ni³na¹, je² Ni³na¹-li⁴, nqui²sa⁴ nˀion¹ tse³ cjoa⁴tsjoa³ xi³ qui³tsjoa³-li² cao⁴-ni³ tsa² mi²yo⁴-li⁴.  
\v 10 Cˀoa⁴tso²: Ji³, Nai³-na¹, sa³ˀnta³ to²tsˀin³-le⁴ cjoa⁴ qui³ni²ntai³ son³ˀnte³, cˀoa⁴ ncˀa³jmi³ tsa³cˀe²nta³-ni³ ntsai⁴.  
\v 11 Je² son³ˀnte³ cao⁴ ncˀa³jmi³ coi⁴xo⁴ya³, to⁴nca³ ji³ to⁴jo³ coi⁴jna³ntsjai²-ni³. Son³ˀnte³ cao⁴ ncˀa³jmi³ coan⁴jchi¹nca³-ni¹ jo³-ni³ tsa² na³jño³.  
\v 12 Cˀoa⁴ cjoa¹xco¹yai³ jo³-ni³ na³jño³jnčho³. Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² cˀoa⁴ntjai²ya³ jo³-ni³ na³jño³. To⁴nca³ ji³ to⁴jo³ ti⁴ji³-ni³, cˀoa⁴ je² no¹-li⁴ a³li² cˀia³ cjoe⁴tˀa³.  
\v 13 Ni³na¹ a³ cˀoa⁴qui³tso²-le⁴ a²ncje⁴ jnco³ cˀa²: Ti⁴jnai³ nca³ qui²xi⁴-na⁴, sa³ˀnta³ nca³ je² xi³ jti³que³-li² coa³tio³nquia³ ntso⁴coi³ jo³-ni³ ya¹te³ xi³ vi³ncha³nai²³.  
\v 14 A³ tsi² tsa² je² nca³tsˀi³ a²ncje⁴ xi³ espíritu xi³ si¹xa¹, xi³ ni²ca³sen¹ nca³ si¹xa¹-le⁴ je² xi³ cˀoai⁴cjoa⁴tjao²-le⁴ cjoa⁴vi³tjo³ntjai². 
\c 2  
\s1 Je² cjoa⁴vi³tjo³ntjai² xi³ nˀion¹ tse³ 
\p  
\v 1 Coi³ je²-vi⁴, tjin¹ne²-na¹ nca³ nqui²sa⁴ nta³ coa⁴sen²sian³² je² cjoa⁴ xi³ qui³no²ˀya², jme¹-ni³ nca³ tsi² tsa² xin² ntia⁴² coan⁴nquin¹-si¹nia³².  
\v 2 Tsa² coan³qui²xi⁴ je² en¹ xi³ qui³tso² je² a²ncje⁴, cˀoa⁴ tsa² qui³tsˀai²-le⁴ cjoa⁴ñˀain³ xi³ tsa³quin²-le⁴ nca³tsˀi³ xi³ tsˀa³ntjai²cjoa⁴, xi³ tsi² qui³si³tjo³son²,  
\v 3 jo¹-sˀin² coi²tjo⁴ntje² nca³ ña¹, tsa² tsi² ma³cjain¹-na¹ cjoa⁴-le⁴ cjoa⁴vi³tjo³ntjai² xi³ nˀion¹ tse³. Je² Nai³-na¹ coan³ti¹tjon² nca³ qui³nchja⁴ya³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ je² cjoa⁴vi³tjo³ntjai². Je² xi³ qui³nčhˀoe¹-le⁴, je²-vi⁴ qui³si³qui²xi⁴ya³-na¹.  
\v 4 Ni³na¹ to⁴jnco³ cao⁴ je² qui³tsjoa³ en¹-le⁴, cao⁴ choa⁴, cao⁴ cjoa⁴xcon¹, cˀoa⁴ cao⁴ cjoa⁴xcon¹ xi³ cja⁴ˀai¹nca¹ tjin¹. Cˀoa⁴ qui³tsjoa³cjoa⁴tjao² je² Espíritu Santo xi³ Ni³na¹ qui³si³cˀa³vi¹son²-le⁴ jo³-sˀin² nca³ me³-le⁴. 
\s1 Jesús nca³jco⁴-le⁴ cjoa⁴vi³tjo³ntjai² 
\p  
\v 5 Nca⁴ tsi² tsa² je² a²ncje⁴ xi³ Ni³na¹ na³nqui³ tsa³cˀe¹jna³-le⁴ je² son³ˀnte³ xi³ cjoa⁴ˀai¹, coi³ xi³ cho³va¹-nia¹.  
\v 6 To⁴nca³ tjin¹ xi³ qui³tsjoa³ en¹-le⁴ ya⁴ jnco³ ˀnte³, qui³tso²: Jme¹-ni³ve⁴ chji¹-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴, nca³ fa³ˀai³tsjen³-ni³li² tˀa³tsˀe⁴, a³xo⁴ je² ˀnti¹-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴, nca³ ˀmi³ cho¹tsen³-lai⁴.  
\v 7 Ji³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² to⁴jnco³ tjo² nqui²sa⁴ na³nqui³ tsa³cˀe²jna³-lai⁴ cao⁴-ni³ tsa² je² a²ncje⁴. Qui³tsˀai²-lai⁴ cjoa⁴je³ya³ cao⁴ cjoa⁴ncˀa³ jo³-ni³ tsa² corona-le⁴. Cˀoa⁴ qui³ni²cˀe¹jna³tˀain³-lai⁴ xa¹-le⁴ ntsai⁴.  
\v 8 Cˀoa⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴ qui³ni²cˀe¹jna³nqui³-lai⁴ nqui³ntso⁴co⁴. Cˀia⁴ nca³ na³nqui³ tsa³cˀe¹jna³-le⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴, ni⁴jme³-jin² xi³ tsa³cˀe¹jna³ xi³ tsi² tsa² na³nqui³ qui³sˀe³jna²-le⁴ nca³ je². To⁴nca³ to⁴jo³ li²coi³ ˀya³² nca³ tjio¹³nqui³-le⁴ nca³tsˀi³, cˀoa⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴.  
\v 9 To⁴nca³ ˀya³-nia¹ je² Jesús xi³ qui³tsˀai²-le⁴ cjoa⁴je³ya³ cao⁴ cjoa⁴ncˀa³ jo³-ni³ tsa² corona-le⁴, nca⁴ tsa³cja³ˀa¹ cjoa⁴ñˀain³ nca³ cˀen³. Je² Jesús xi³ to⁴jnco³ tjo² nqui²sa⁴ na³nqui³ coan³ cao⁴-ni³ tsa² a²ncje⁴, jme¹-ni³ nca³ to⁴cjoa⁴nta³-le⁴ Ni³na¹ qui³sco²tˀa³-si¹ni³ cjoa⁴vi³ya³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ nca³tsˀi³.  
\v 10 Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² tjin¹ nca³yi³je³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹. Je² xi³ tsa³cˀe¹nta³ nca³yi³je³. Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² tsa³quin²-le⁴ Ni³na¹, cˀia⁴ nca³ ja³ˀai³cao⁴ ncjin² xti³ xi³ vˀa³cao⁴-le⁴ cjoa⁴je³ya³-le⁴, nca³ ña³qui³ qui³si³jnco³-ni³ cao⁴ cjoa⁴ñˀain³ je² xi³ nca³jco⁴-le⁴ cjoa⁴vi³tjo³ntjai²-le⁴.  
\v 11 Je² Jesús xi³ si¹tsje³, cˀoa⁴ je² cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ xi³ ti¹ni²tsje³, nca³tsˀi³ tsˀe⁴ to⁴jnco³ je² Ni³na¹. Coi³ li²coi³ ma³soa³-le⁴ Jesús nca³ ntsˀe⁴ tso²-le⁴.  
\v 12 Cˀoa⁴tso²: Coi³nchja²ya³-ni³le⁴ ntsˀe³ je² jan³ˀain¹-li⁴, ya⁴jin³-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴-na⁴ cˀoa³sje³nta³-le²³.  
\v 13 Nqui²jnco³cˀa² tso²: An³ nta³ nˀion¹tˀa³coan³ nca³ je². Cˀoa⁴ nqui²jnco³cˀa² tso²: Coe⁴-ni³, an³ cao⁴ je² xti³ xi³ qui³tsjoa³-na³ Ni³na¹.  
\v 14 To⁴jo³-sˀin² nca³ je² xti³ qui³sˀe³-le⁴ yao³ cao⁴ njin¹, cˀoa⁴-ti⁴sˀin² qui³sˀe³-le⁴ nca³ je² xi³ ti⁴coi³-ni³, jme¹-ni³ nca³ si⁴²cje³tˀa³-si¹ni³, to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ cjoa⁴vi³ya³-le⁴, je² xi³ tsa³ca³te¹xo³ma³ cjoa⁴vi³ya³, xi³ coi³ nai⁴²,  
\v 15 cˀoa⁴ jme¹-ni³ nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² si⁴²ca³tio¹ntai¹-ni³ je² xi³ tsa³ca³tio²xcon¹ nca³ qui³tsa³cjon¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴vi³ya³ jo³ tjin¹ ni⁴čhjin³ tsa³ca³tio²con³.  
\v 16 Xi³ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ Jesús li²coi³ qui³scoe¹ a²ncje⁴ nca³ cˀoa⁴sje³ntjai², to⁴nca³ qui³scoe¹ ntje⁴-le⁴ Abraham nca³ cˀoa⁴sje³ntjai².  
\v 17 To⁴coi³ nca³ ña³qui³ coan³chjen¹-le⁴ nca³ cˀoa⁴ cjoan³ jo³ cjoan³ ntsˀe⁴, to⁴nca³yi³je³-ni³ cjoa⁴, jme¹-ni³ nca³ cˀoa⁴sˀin² coan⁴-si¹ni³ na⁴ˀmi³ti¹tjon² xi³ tjin¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴ma⁴ta³con², xi³ nta³ si¹tjo³son² nca³yi³je³ jña³-le⁴ xi³ tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹, nca³ cˀoe⁴²chji¹ntjai² je¹-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴.  
\v 18 Jo³-sˀin² nca³ ti⁴je²-ni³ qui³cho²tˀa³ nca³ tsa³cja³ˀa¹ cjoa⁴ñˀain³, cˀoa⁴-ti⁴sˀin² ma³-le⁴ va³sen¹cao⁴ je² xi³ cho¹tˀa³-ni³ cjoa⁴ñˀain³. 
\c 3  
\s1 Jesús nqui²sa⁴ tse³ cjoa⁴je³ya³ va³quin²-le⁴ cao⁴-ni³ tsa² Moisés 
\p  
\v 1 To⁴coi³ ntsˀe³ xi³ tsje³ cjoaon³, jon² xi³ cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ tsa³cja³ˀa¹jin³-no³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ ntia⁴² xi³ tsˀe⁴ ncˀa³jmi³, nta³ ti⁴cja³ˀai³tsjen³jion³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ je² Cristo Jesús xi³ pa²stro⁴-le⁴, cˀoa⁴ na⁴ˀmi³ti¹tjon²-le⁴ je² cjoa⁴ xi³ ni²qui²xi⁴ya³nta³-nia¹.  
