\v 3 Nqui²sa⁴ tse³ cjoa⁴je³ya³ va³quin²-le⁴ Jesús cao⁴-ni³ tsa² Moisés, jo³-sˀin² nca³ je² xi³ tsa³cˀe¹nta³ jnco³ ntˀia³ nqui²sa⁴ tjin¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴je³ya³ cao⁴-ni³ tsa² ntˀia³.  
\v 4 Nca³yi³je³ ntˀia³ tjin¹ jnco³ xi³ vˀe¹nta³, to⁴nca³ je² xi³ tsa³cˀe¹nta³ nca³yi³je³, je² Ni³na¹.  
\v 5 Xi³ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ je² Moisés nta³ qui³si³tjo³son² xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ nca³tsˀi³ cho⁴ta⁴ni³ˀya³-le⁴ Ni³na¹, jo³-ni³ cho⁴ˀnta³, nca³ qui³tsjoa³ en¹-le⁴ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ cjoa⁴ xi³ coan⁴scan³-ni³ coi⁴no²cjoa⁴ya³.  
